3. The Prophet Jeremy doth expresse it as the Happy Condition of Gospell-times, that they should sweare,Jer. 5.2.
               the Lord liveth, in Truth, in Righteousnesse, and Judgment. i. Not that they should utterly absteine from Oathes, but use them with due Care and Circumspection;

fully understanding what and why the sweare.
